# Development Branch Notes

## Branch Purpose

### main

* Stable branch containing completed and tested project work.

### dev

* Development branch used for planning, documentation, and integrating new features before merging into the main branch.

### sensor-module

* Contains code related to IoT sensors such as temperature, humidity, ultrasonic, PIR, gas, and light sensors.

### wireless-module

* Contains code related to wireless communication technologies including Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, BLE, ESP-NOW, MQTT, and LoRa.
